Holy Sanctuary makes it easy to get plugged in to the Bible. Experience the refreshing, life-changing power of Scripture in this state-of-the-art digital sound recording, mastered for optimum listening clarity. This recording is dramatized for additional impact and interest. The New Living Translation uses language that speaks to the heart and is intended to be read aloud, making Holy Sanctuary the perfect audio companion for driving, walking, or wherever you enjoy listening to Scripture.
